## id: gitblit-panel
## name: Gitblit Login Panel - Detect
## author: hack007x
## severity: info
## tags: panel,gitblit,discovery
## description: Gitblit login panel was detected — a pure Java stack for managing, viewing, and serving Git repositories.
## affects: gitblit
## reference: https://www.gitblit.com/
